Meet Ms. Octavia! Yes, she is the mother of JT, from the City Girls. She is also a Philanthropist and Activist! ❤️ Ms. Octavia is the founder of @after_the_sentence, a non profit organization for women transitioning from jail or prison to society.
 I’m so honored, because Ms. Octavia had the opportunity to speak with a group of young girls yesterday, and she read them my Tell Somebody children’s book! She taught them that even if somebody threatens to harm them or their family, they still need to speak up and tell somebody if they are being touched inappropriately. A young girl then raised her hand and asked, “What if she tells a person who doesn’t care, and doesn’t do anything to help her?” The answer… to keep telling, until someone does help! Thank you @newbeginings_4, for helping spread awareness about child abuse, and helping save lives!! ❤️
